description: PIMS 3571 CC MSP: Building Energy Efficiency Project

subproject.corporate outcome: Environmental governance improved for effective management of natural resources, and, better access to priority environmental services.
subproject.description:
1. Policy and institutional development enhanced regarding new energy efficiency Building codes norms and standards
2. Modern energy efficient construction technologies applied.
3. Energy Conservation knowledge of homeowners, construction sector professionals, and relevant government personnel enhanced
4. Financing Support provided to those interested in energy efficiency in their dwellings
